<h1 id="ä¸­æ€§å­æ˜Ÿã®æŒ¯å‹•">ä¸­æ€§å­æ˜Ÿã®æŒ¯å‹•</h1>

<p>å®Ÿéš›ã®ä¸­æ€§å­æ˜Ÿã¯å›ºä½“ã‚¯ãƒ©ã‚¹ãƒˆã‚„å¼·ã„ç£å ´ã€è¶…æµå‹•ã‚„é«˜é€Ÿè‡ªè»¢ãªã©ã®ç‰¹å¾´ã‚’æŒã¤ãŸã‚ã€ä¸­æ€§å­æ˜Ÿã®æŒ¯å‹•ãƒ¢ãƒ¼ãƒ‰ã¯è¤‡é›‘ã‚’æ¥µã‚ã¾ã™ã€‚
åŠ ãˆã¦ã€ä¸­æ€§å­æ˜Ÿã¯ä¸€èˆ¬ç›¸å¯¾è«–çš„ãªåŠ¹æœãŒé‡è¦ã¨ãªã‚‹å¤©ä½“ã§ã‚ã‚‹ãŸã‚ã€ä¸€èˆ¬ç›¸å¯¾è«–ã®æ çµ„ã¿ã‚’ç”¨ã„ãŸæŒ¯å‹•ã®æ‰±ã„ãŒå¿…è¦ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ä¾‹ãˆã°ã€ä¸­æ€§å­æ˜Ÿã®æŒ¯å‹•ã«ã‚ˆã‚Šé‡åŠ›æ³¢ãŒç™ºç”Ÿã—ã€ãã‚ŒãŒç„¡é™é ã«é£›ã³å»ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã§ä¸­æ€§å­æ˜ŸæŒ¯å‹•ãŒæ¸›è¡°ã™ã‚‹åŠ¹æœãªã©ãŒç¾ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚
ãã“ã§ã“ã“ã§ã¯ã€ã“ã®ã‚ˆã†ãªè¤‡é›‘ãªç‰©ç†ã¯è€ƒãˆãšã€ä¸­æ€§å­æ˜Ÿã®å¾®å°æŒ¯å¹…æŒ¯å‹•ã‚’æ™®é€šã®æ’æ˜Ÿã®æŒ¯å‹•ãƒ¢ãƒ¼ãƒ‰è§£æã¨åŒæ§˜ã«è¦‹ã¦ã„ãã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚<br />
æ™®é€šã®æ’æ˜Ÿã®æ™®é€šã®ãƒ¢ãƒ¼ãƒ‰ã¯ã€ä¸€èˆ¬çš„ã« p-, f-, g- ã®3ã¤ã®ãƒ¢ãƒ¼ãƒ‰ã«åˆ†é¡ã•ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚
p-modeã¯æµä½“ã®åœ§ç¸®æ€§(ã™ãªã‚ã¡åœ§åŠ›)ãŒå¾©å…ƒåŠ›ã¨ãªã£ã¦æŒ¯å‹•ã™ã‚‹ãƒ¢ãƒ¼ãƒ‰ã§ã€ãã®æŒ¯å‹•å‘¨æ³¢æ•°ã¯é«˜å‘¨æ³¢ã¨ãªã‚‹å‚¾å‘ã«ã‚ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
æ¬¡ã«ã€g-modeã¯æµ®åŠ›(ã™ãªã‚ã¡é‡åŠ›)ãŒå¾©å…ƒåŠ›ã¨ãªã£ã¦æŒ¯å‹•ã™ã‚‹ãƒ¢ãƒ¼ãƒ‰ã§ã€p-modeã«æ¯”ã¹ã¦ä½å‘¨æ³¢ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
æ’æ˜ŸãŒé«˜é€Ÿå›è»¢ã—ã¦ã„ã‚‹å ´åˆã€ã‚³ãƒªã‚ªãƒªåŠ›ãŒå¾©å…ƒåŠ›ã¨ã—ã¦åƒãå›è»¢ãƒ¢ãƒ¼ãƒ‰ã¨æ…£æ€§ãƒ¢ãƒ¼ãƒ‰ãŒç¾ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚
ã•ã‚‰ã«å›ºä½“ã‚¯ãƒ©ã‚¹ãƒˆãŒå­˜åœ¨ã™ã‚‹å ´åˆã€éŸ³æ³¢ãŒã‚¯ãƒ©ã‚¹ãƒˆä¸­ã‚’ä¼æ’­ã™ã‚‹åŠ¹æœã‚‚ç¾ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚
ãã—ã¦å¼·ç£å ´ãŒã‚ã‚‹å ´åˆã€ã‚¢ãƒ«ãƒ´ã‚§ãƒ¼ãƒ³æ³¢ã«ã‚ˆã‚‹æŒ¯å‹•ã‚‚è€ƒæ…®ã™ã‚‹å¿…è¦ãŒã‚ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<h2 id="å›è»¢ãªã—ç£å ´ãªã—ã®é€šå¸¸ã®æ’æ˜Ÿã®é€šå¸¸ã®æŒ¯å‹•ãƒ¢ãƒ¼ãƒ‰">å›è»¢ãªã—ãƒ»ç£å ´ãªã—ã®é€šå¸¸ã®æ’æ˜Ÿã®é€šå¸¸ã®æŒ¯å‹•ãƒ¢ãƒ¼ãƒ‰</h2>

<p>ã“ã“ã§ã¯ç°¡å˜ã®ãŸã‚ã€æŒ¯å‹•ã¯æ–­ç†±ã¨ã—ã€ç²˜æ€§ã¯è€ƒãˆãªã„ã¨ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
ã•ã‚‰ã«æ’æ˜Ÿã¯é«˜é€Ÿè‡ªè»¢ã‚‚ç£å ´ã‚‚ãªã„ã¨ã—ã¦ã€é‡åŠ›ã‚‚ãƒ‹ãƒ¥ãƒ¼ãƒˆãƒ³é‡åŠ›ã§è€ƒãˆã‚‹ã“ã¨ã«ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚
ã™ã‚‹ã¨ã€ã“ã®ç³»ã‚’è¨˜è¿°ã™ã‚‹æ–¹ç¨‹å¼ã¯ã€ä»¥ä¸‹ã§ä¸ãˆã‚‰ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

\[\frac{\partial \rho}{\partial t} + \nabla \cdot (\rho \mathbf{v}) 
= 0 \tag{1}\]

\[\rho \frac{d \mathbf{v}}{dt} 
= - \nabla P - \rho \nabla \Phi \tag{2}\]

\[\nabla^2 \Phi 
= 4\pi G \rho \tag{3}\]

\[\rho T \frac{ds}{dt} 
= \rho \epsilon - \nabla \cdot \mathbf{F} \tag{4}\]

\[\mathbf{F}_\mathrm{rad} 
= -\lambda_\mathrm{rad} \nabla T \tag{5}\]

<p>ã“ã“ã§\(\Phi\)ã¯é‡åŠ›ãƒãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚·ãƒ£ãƒ«ã€\(s\)ã¯å˜ä½è³ªé‡ã‚ãŸã‚Šã®ã‚¨ãƒ³ãƒˆãƒ­ãƒ”ãƒ¼ã€\(\epsilon\)ã¯ã‚¨ãƒãƒ«ã‚®ãƒ¼ç”Ÿæˆç‡ã€\(\mathbf{F}_\mathrm{rad}\)ã¯æ”¾å°„ã«ã‚ˆã‚‹ã‚¨ãƒãƒ«ã‚®ãƒ¼æµæŸã§ã™ã€‚
ãã—ã¦\(\mathbf{F} = \mathbf{F}_\mathrm{rad} + \mathbf{F}_\mathrm{conv}\)ã§ã‚ã‚Šã€\(\mathbf{F}_\mathrm{conv}\)ã¯å¯¾æµã«ã‚ˆã‚‹ã‚¨ãƒãƒ«ã‚®ãƒ¼æµæŸã‚’è¡¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚<br />
æ–­ç†±ãªæŒ¯å‹•ã‚’ä»®å®šã—ã€ã•ã‚‰ã«é‡åŠ›ãƒãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚·ãƒ£ãƒ«ã®æ‘‚å‹•ã¯ç„¡è¦–ã§ãã‚‹ã¨ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
å¯†åº¦ãƒ»é€Ÿåº¦ãƒ»åœ§åŠ›ã®æ‘‚å‹•é‡ã‚’ãã‚Œãã‚Œ\(\rho', \mathbf{v}', P'\)ã—ã€(1), (2), (4)å¼ã‚’ç·šå½¢åŒ–ã—ã¦ã„ãã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
(1)å¼ã‹ã‚‰</p>

\[\begin{align}
\frac{\partial}{\partial t} ( \rho + \rho') + \nabla \cdot \{(\rho + \rho') (\mathbf{v} + \mathbf{v}')\} 
&amp;= \frac{\partial \rho}{\partial t} + \frac{\partial \rho'}{\partial t} + \nabla \cdot (\rho \mathbf{v}) + \nabla \cdot (\rho \mathbf{v}') + \nabla \cdot (\rho' \mathbf{v}) \notag \\
&amp;\underbrace{=}_{(1)} \frac{\partial \rho'}{\partial t} + \nabla \cdot (\rho \mathbf{v}' + \rho' \mathbf{v}) 
= 0 \tag{6} 
\end{align}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
(2)å¼ã®å·¦è¾ºã¯</p>

\[\begin{align}
(\rho + \rho' )\frac{d}{dt} (\mathbf{v} + \mathbf{v}') 
&amp;= \rho \left[ \frac{\partial}{\partial t} + \{ (\mathbf{v} + \mathbf{v}') \cdot \nabla \} \right] (\mathbf{v} + \mathbf{v}')+ \rho' \frac{d \mathbf{v}}{dt} \notag \\
&amp;= \rho \left[ \frac{\partial \mathbf{v}}{\partial t} + \{ (\mathbf{v} + \mathbf{v}' )\cdot \nabla \} \mathbf{v} \right] + \rho \left\{ \frac{\partial \mathbf{v}'}{\partial t} + (\mathbf{v} \cdot \nabla) \mathbf{v}'\right\} + \rho' \frac{d \mathbf{v}}{dt} \notag \\
&amp;= \rho \frac{d \mathbf{v}}{dt} + \rho' \frac{d \mathbf{v}}{dt} + \rho \left\{ \frac{\partial \mathbf{v}'}{\partial t} + (\mathbf{v}' \cdot \nabla) \mathbf{v} + (\mathbf{v} \cdot \nabla) \mathbf{v}'\right\} \notag 
\end{align}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚‹ãŸã‚ã€æœ€çµ‚çš„ã«</p>

\[\rho' \frac{d \mathbf{v}}{dt} + \rho \left\{ \frac{\partial \mathbf{v}'}{\partial t} + (\mathbf{v}' \cdot \nabla) \mathbf{v} + (\mathbf{v} \cdot \nabla) \mathbf{v}'\right\} 
= - \nabla P' - \rho' \nabla \Phi \tag{7}\]

<p>ã‚’å¾—ã¾ã™ã€‚æ–­ç†±çš„ãªæ‘‚å‹•ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã¨ã—ã¦ã€\(T ds = dQ = 0\)ã¨ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\begin{align}
\frac{dQ}{dt} 
&amp;= \frac{de}{dt} + P \frac{dV}{dt} 
= \frac{dP}{dt} \left( \frac{de}{dP}\right)_\rho + \frac{d\rho}{dt} \left(\frac{de}{d\rho} \right)_P + P \frac{d}{dt} \left( \frac{1}{\rho} \right) \notag \\
&amp;= \frac{dP}{dt} \left( \frac{de}{dP}\right)_\rho + \frac{d\rho}{dt} \left(\frac{de}{d\rho} \right)_P - \frac{P}{\rho^2} \frac{d \rho}{dt} 
= \left( \frac{de}{dP} \right)_\rho \left\{ \frac{dP}{dt} - \frac{\frac{P}{\rho^2} - \left( \frac{de}{d\rho} \right)_P}{\left( \frac{de}{dP}\right)_P}\frac{d\rho}{dt}\right\} 
= 0 \notag
\end{align}\]

<p>ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\frac{dP}{dt} 
= \frac{\frac{P}{\rho^2} - \left( \frac{de}{d\rho} \right)_P}{\left( \frac{de}{dP}\right)_P}\frac{d\rho}{dt} 
\equiv \left( \frac{\partial P}{\partial \rho} \right)_\mathrm{ad} \frac{d\rho}{dt}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã‚Œã‚’\(P \rightarrow P + P', \rho \rightarrow \rho + \rho'\)ã¨ã—ã¦ã€ç·šå½¢åŒ–ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚</p>

\[\begin{aligned}
\frac{d}{dt} (P + P') 
&amp;= \frac{\partial P}{\partial t} + \{ (\mathbf{v} + \mathbf{v}') \cdot \nabla \} P + \frac{\partial P'}{\partial t} + (\mathbf{v} \cdot \nabla) P' \\
&amp;= \frac{\partial P}{\partial t} + ( \mathbf{v} \cdot \nabla) P + \frac{\partial P'}{\partial t} + (\mathbf{v}' \cdot \nabla) P + (\mathbf{v} \cdot \nabla) P' 
\end{aligned}\]

<p>ã‚ˆã‚Šã€æœ€çµ‚çš„ã«</p>

\[\frac{\partial P'}{\partial t} + (\mathbf{v}' \cdot \nabla) P + (\mathbf{v} \cdot \nabla) P' 
= \left( \frac{\partial P}{\partial \rho} \right)_\mathrm{ad} \left( \frac{\partial \rho'}{\partial t} + (\mathbf{v}' \cdot \nabla) \rho + (\mathbf{v} \cdot \nabla) \rho' \right) \tag{8}\]

<p>ã‚’å¾—ã¾ã™ã€‚<br />
ã“ã“ã§æ‘‚å‹•é‡ã®æ™‚é–“ä¾å­˜æ€§ã¯\(e^{i\omega t}\)ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã¨ã—ã€ã•ã‚‰ã«å¹³è¡¡çŠ¶æ…‹ã¯\(\mathbf{v}=\mathbf{0}\)ã‹ã¤çƒå¯¾ç§°ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã¨ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
æœ€å¾Œã«\(\mathbf{v}' = i\omega \boldsymbol{\xi}\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ã€å¤‰ä½ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«\(\boldsymbol{\xi}\)ã‚’å®šã‚ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[(6) \ \Longrightarrow \ 
\rho' + \nabla \cdot (\rho \boldsymbol{\xi}) 
= 0 \tag{9}\]

<p>å¹³è¡¡çŠ¶æ…‹ã§ã¯ã€\(-\nabla P - \rho \nabla \Phi = \mathbf{0}\)ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[(7) \ \Longrightarrow \ 
i \omega \rho \frac{\partial \boldsymbol{\xi}}{\partial t} 
= - \nabla P' - \rho' \nabla \Phi \ \Longrightarrow \ 
-\omega^2 \boldsymbol{\xi} + \frac{1}{\rho} \nabla P' - \frac{\rho'}{\rho^2} \nabla P 
= \mathbf{0} \tag{10}\]

<p>(8)å¼ã®å·¦è¾ºã¯</p>

\[\frac{\partial \rho'}{\partial t} + (\mathbf{v}' \cdot \nabla) \rho + (\mathbf{v} \cdot \nabla) \rho' 
= i\omega \rho' + i\omega (\boldsymbol{\xi} \cdot \nabla) \rho 
= i\omega \rho \left( \frac{\rho'}{\rho} + \xi_r \frac{d\ln \rho}{dr} \right)\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ•´ç†ã•ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚
é€”ä¸­ã€å¹³è¡¡çŠ¶æ…‹ãŒçƒå¯¾ç§°ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‹ã‚‰ã€\(\rho(r)\)ã¨ã—ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚
å³è¾ºã«ã‚‚åŒæ§˜ã®å¤‰å½¢ã‚’è¡Œã†ã¨</p>

\[\begin{align}
(8) &amp; \Longrightarrow \ 
P \left( \frac{P'}{P} + \xi_r \frac{d\ln P}{dr} \right) 
= \left( \frac{\partial P}{\partial \rho}\right)_\mathrm{ad} \rho \left( \frac{\rho'}{\rho} + \xi_r \frac{d\ln \rho}{dr} \right) \notag \\
&amp; \Longrightarrow \ 
\frac{P'}{P} + \xi_r \frac{d\ln P}{dr} 
= \Gamma_1 \left( \frac{\rho'}{\rho} + \xi_r \frac{d\ln \rho}{dr} \right) \tag{11}
\end{align}\]

<p>é€”ä¸­</p>

\[\Gamma_1 
\equiv \left( \frac{\partial \ln P}{\partial \ln \rho}\right)_\mathrm{ad} 
= \frac{\rho}{P} \left( \frac{\partial P}{\partial \rho}\right)_\mathrm{ad} \tag{12}\]

<p>ã¨ã—ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚<br />
çƒå¯¾ç§°ãªå¤©ä½“ã«ã¤ã„ã¦è€ƒãˆã‚‹ãŸã‚ã€ä»¥é™ã§ã¯æ¥µåº§æ¨™ç³» \((r, \theta, \varphi)\)ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã«ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
ãã—ã¦ã€å¤‰ä½ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«\(\boldsymbol{\xi}\)ã‚’ã€ä»¥ä¸‹ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«\(r\)ã¨\((\theta, \varphi)\)ã§å¤‰æ•°åˆ†é›¢ã—ã¦ã¿ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

\[\boldsymbol{\xi} 
= \xi_r (r) \mathbf{e}_r + \xi_H (r) \nabla_H Y_\ell^m + \xi_T(r) (\mathbf{e}_r \times \nabla_H Y_\ell^m) \tag{13}\]

<p>ã“ã“ã§\(Y_\ell^m = Y_\ell^m (\theta, \varphi)\)ã¯<a href="/math/spherical">çƒé¢èª¿å’Œé–¢æ•°</a>ã§ã‚ã‚Š</p>

\[\nabla_H 
= \mathbf{e}_\theta \frac{\partial}{\partial \theta} + \mathbf{e}_\varphi \frac{1}{\sin \theta} \frac{\partial}{\partial \varphi} \tag{14}\]

<p>ã§ã™ã€‚
ã•ã‚‰ã«</p>

\[\mathbf{e}_r \cdot (\nabla_H Y_\ell^m)
 = \nabla_H Y_\ell^m \cdot (\mathbf{e}_r \times \nabla_H Y_\ell^m) 
 = \mathbf{e}_r \cdot (\mathbf{e}_r \times \nabla_H Y_\ell^m) 
 = 0 \tag{15}\]

<p>ãŒæˆã‚Šç«‹ã¡ã¾ã™ã€‚
ã¾ãŸã‚¹ã‚«ãƒ©ãƒ¼é‡ã®æ‘‚å‹•ã«ã¤ã„ã¦ã¯</p>

\[P' 
= P_A'(r) Y_\ell^m, \quad \rho' 
= \rho_A'(r) Y_\ell^m \tag{16}\]

<p>ã¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚
(10)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\begin{align}
&amp;-\omega^2 \{\xi_r \mathbf{e}_r + \xi_H \nabla_H Y_\ell^m + \xi_T (\mathbf{e}_r \times \nabla_H Y_\ell^m )\} + \frac{1}{\rho} \left( \mathbf{e}_r \frac{\partial}{\partial r} + \frac{1}{r} \nabla_H \right) P_A' Y_\ell^m - \frac{\rho_A' Y_\ell^m}{\rho^2} \left( \mathbf{e}_r \frac{\partial}{\partial r} + \frac{1}{r} \nabla_H \right) P \notag \\
&amp;= \left( -\omega^2 \xi_r + \frac{1}{\rho} \frac{dP'}{dr} - \frac{\rho'}{\rho^2} \frac{dP}{dr} \right) \mathbf{e}_r + \left( - \omega^2 \xi_H + \frac{P_A'}{r\rho} \right) \nabla_H Y_\ell^m - \omega^2 \xi_T (\mathbf{e}_r \times \nabla_H Y_\ell^m) 
= \mathbf{0} \notag 
\end{align}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«è¨ˆç®—ã•ã‚Œã‚‹ãŸã‚ã€å„æˆåˆ†ã‹ã‚‰</p>

\[-\omega^2 \xi_r + \frac{1}{\rho} \frac{dP'}{dr} - \frac{\rho'}{\rho^2} \frac{dP}{dr} 
= 0 \tag{17}\]

\[-\omega^2 \xi_H + \frac{P_A'}{r \rho} 
= 0 \tag{18}\]

\[-\omega^2 \xi_T 
= 0 \tag{19}\]

<p>ã¨ã‚ã‹ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã“ã‹ã‚‰ã€\(\omega \neq 0\)ã®æ³¢ã§ã¯ã€å¸¸ã«\(\xi_T = 0\)ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã‚ã‹ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚<br />
\(\boldsymbol{\xi} = \xi_r \mathbf{e}_r + \xi_H \nabla_H Y_\ell^m\)ã‚’spheroidal modesã€ãã—ã¦\(\boldsymbol{\xi} = \xi_T (\mathbf{e}_r \times \nabla_H Y_\ell^m)\)ã‚’toroidal modesã¨å‘¼ã³ã¾ã™ã€‚
è‡ªè»¢ã—ã¦ã„ãªã„æ’æ˜Ÿã§ã¯ã€spheroidal modesã¨toroidal modesã¯2ã¤ã«åˆ†é›¢ã™ã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã€ã•ã‚‰ã«å…ˆã»ã©ã®è­°è«–ã‹ã‚‰\(\xi_T = 0\)ã¨ãªã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã‚ã‹ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
\(\omega =0\)ã§ã¯ä»»æ„ã®\(\xi_T\)ãŒè¨±ã•ã‚Œã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‹ã‚‰ã€è‡ªè»¢ã®ãªã„æ’æ˜Ÿã§ã¯ã€\(\omega = 0\)ã®toridal modesãŒç¸®é€€ã—ã¦ã„ã‚‹ã¨è€ƒãˆã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‚‚ã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚<br />
\(\omega \neq 0\)ã«å¯¾ã™ã‚‹å¼å¤‰å½¢ã‚’é€²ã‚ã¦ã„ãã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
(17)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\frac{dP'}{dr} 
= \rho \omega^2 \xi_r + \frac{\rho'}{\rho} \frac{dP}{dr} \notag\]

<p>ã“ã“ã§ã€(2)å¼ã¨ã€å¹³è¡¡çŠ¶æ…‹ã§ã¯å¸¸ã«\(\mathbf{v}=0\)ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‹ã‚‰</p>

\[\frac{dP}{dr} 
= \rho \frac{d\Phi}{dr} 
= \frac{GM_r \rho}{r^2} 
= \rho g \quad \left( g = \frac{GM_r}{r^2} \right) \tag{20}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
é€”ä¸­ã€ä¸­å¿ƒã‹ã‚‰è·é›¢\(r\)ã®ä½ç½®ã§ã®é‡åŠ›ãƒãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚·ãƒ£ãƒ«ã‚’\(\Phi = -\frac{GM_r}{r}\)ã¨ã—ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚
ã•ã‚‰ã«(11)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\frac{\rho'}{\rho} 
= \frac{1}{\Gamma_1} \left( \frac{P'}{P} + \xi_r \frac{d\ln P}{dr}\right) - \xi_r \frac{d \ln \rho}{dr} \tag{21}\]

<p>ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\begin{align}
\frac{dP'}{dr} 
&amp;= \rho \omega^2 \xi_r + \frac{\rho g}{\Gamma_1} \left( \frac{P'}{P} + \xi_r \frac{d\ln P}{dr}\right) - \xi_r \rho g \frac{d\ln \rho}{dr} \notag \\
&amp;= \rho \xi_r \left\{ \omega^2 - g \left( \frac{d\ln \rho}{dr} - \frac{1}{\Gamma_1} \frac{d\ln P}{dr} \right) \right\} + \frac{1}{\Gamma_1} \frac{d\ln P}{dr} P' \tag{22}
\end{align}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã“ã§ã€ä»¥ä¸‹ã®é‡ã‚’å®šç¾©ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚</p>

\[N^2 
= -gA, \quad
A 
\equiv \frac{d \ln \rho}{dr} - \frac{1}{\Gamma_1} \frac{d \ln P}{dr} \tag{23}\]

<p>ã“ã®\(N\)ã¯ãƒ–ãƒ©ãƒ³ãƒˆãƒ»ãƒã‚¤ã‚µãƒ©æŒ¯å‹•æ•° (Brunt-VÃ¤isÃ¤lÃ¤ frequency)ã¨å‘¼ã°ã‚Œã€æ’æ˜Ÿç‰©ç†ã«é™ã‚‰ãšã€é‡åŠ›ã¨æµ®åŠ›ã‚’å¾©å…ƒåŠ›ã¨ã—ãŸæ³¢å‹•ç¾è±¡ã«ãŠã„ã¦ç¾ã‚Œã‚‹æŒ¯å‹•æ•°ã§ã™ã€‚
ã“ã‚Œã‚’ç”¨ã„ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\frac{dP_A'}{dr} 
= \frac{1}{\Gamma_1} \frac{d\ln P}{dr} P' + \rho (\omega^2 - N^2) \xi_r \tag{24}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ•´ç†ã•ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚
ã•ã‚‰ã«(9)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\rho' + \nabla \cdot {\rho \boldsymbol{\xi}} 
= \rho' + \boldsymbol{\xi} \cdot (\nabla \rho) + \rho (\nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{\xi}) 
= 0\]

<p>ç¬¬ä¸‰é …ã‚’è¨ˆç®—ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚</p>

\[\begin{aligned}
\nabla \cdot \boldsymbol{\xi} 
&amp;= \left( \mathbf{e}_r \frac{\partial}{\partial r} + \frac{1}{r} \nabla_H \right) \cdot \{ \xi_r \mathbf{e}_r + \xi_H \nabla_H Y_\ell^m + \xi_T (\mathbf{e}_r \times \nabla_H Y_\ell^m) \} 
= \frac{d \xi_r}{dr} + \frac{\xi_H}{r} \nabla_H^2 Y_\ell^m \\
&amp;= \frac{d \xi_r}{dr} - \frac{\xi_H \ell (\ell + 1)}{r} Y_\ell^m
\end{aligned}\]

<p>æœ€å¾Œã®ç­‰å·ã§ã¯ã€<a href="/math/spherical">çƒé¢èª¿å’Œé–¢æ•°ã®æ€§è³ª\(\nabla_H^2 Y_\ell^m = - \ell (\ell + 1) Y_\ell^m\)</a>ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚
ä»¥ä¸Šã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\begin{aligned}
\rho' + \xi_r \frac{d\rho}{dr} + \rho \frac{d\xi_r}{dr} - \frac{\rho \xi_H \ell (\ell + 1)}{r} Y_\ell^m 
&amp;\underbrace{=}_{(21)} \frac{\rho}{\Gamma_1} \left( \frac{P'}{P} + \xi_r \frac{d\ln P}{dr}\right) - \rho \xi_r \frac{d\ln \rho}{dr} + \xi_r \frac{d\rho}{dr} + \rho \frac{d\xi_r}{dr} - \frac{\rho \xi_H \ell (\ell + 1)}{r} Y_\ell^m \\
&amp;\underbrace{=}_{(18)} \frac{\rho}{\Gamma_1} \left( \frac{P'}{P} + \xi_r \frac{d\ln P}{dr}\right) + \rho \frac{d\xi_r}{dr} - \frac{\ell (\ell + 1) P_A'}{r^2 \omega^2} Y_\ell^m 
= 0 
\end{aligned}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ã•ã‚‰ã«</p>

\[S_\ell^2 
\equiv \frac{\ell (\ell+1)}{r^2} a^2, \quad a^2 
= \frac{\Gamma_1 P}{\rho} \tag{25}\]

<p>ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã€å¼ã‚’æ•´ç†ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\frac{d\xi_r}{dr} 
= \left( \frac{S_\ell^2}{\omega^2} - 1\right) \frac{P'}{\Gamma_1 P} - \frac{1}{\Gamma_1} \frac{d \ln P}{dr} \xi_r \tag{26}\]

<p>ã‚’å¾—ã¾ã™ã€‚
\(S_\ell\)ã¯ãƒ©ãƒ å‘¨æ³¢æ•° (Lamb frequency)ã¨å‘¼ã°ã‚Œã€éŸ³é€ŸãŒçƒé¢ä¸Šã®æ³¢é•·ã‚’æ¨ªåˆ‡ã‚‹æ™‚é–“ã®é€†æ•°ã¨ã—ã¦å®šç¾©ã•ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚<br />
å‘¨æ³¢æ•°\(\omega\)ã®å›ºæœ‰å€¤å•é¡Œã¨ã—ã¦ã€(24), (26)å¼ã®é€£ç«‹å¾®åˆ†æ–¹ç¨‹å¼ã‚’é©åˆ‡ãª(æ’æ˜Ÿä¸­å¿ƒéƒ¨ã¨æ’æ˜Ÿè¡¨é¢ã§ã®)å¢ƒç•Œæ¡ä»¶ã§è§£ãã“ã¨ã§ã€ã©ã®ã‚ˆã†ãªæŒ¯å‹•ãŒå­˜åœ¨ã™ã‚‹ã‹ã‚’çŸ¥ã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚
\(N^2 &gt;0\)ã®å ´åˆã€å®‰å®šã—ãŸæµä½“ã®æµ®åŠ›æŒ¯å‹•ã®ãŸã‚ã«ã€ã‚¨ãƒãƒ«ã‚®ãƒ¼ã¯è¼»å°„ã«ã‚ˆã£ã¦é‹ã°ã‚Œã¾ã™ (radiative regionsã€‚)
ä¸€æ–¹ã€\(N^2 &lt; 0\)ã®å ´åˆã€ã“ã‚Œã¯æµä½“ãŒä¸Šæ˜‡/ä¸‹é™ã‚’ç¶šã‘ã‚‹å¯¾æµå±¤ã‚’è¡¨ã—ã¾ã™ (convective retionsã€‚)
\(\omega^2 \gg N^2, S_\ell^2\)ã¯p-modesã§ã‚ã‚Šã€\(\omega^2 \ll N^2, S_\ell^2\)ã¯g-modesã§ã™ã€‚</p>

