\[E 
= \frac{1}{2} \int \left\{ \rho \delta \mathbf{v} \cdot \delta \mathbf{v} + \left( \frac{\delta P}{\rho} + \delta \Phi \right) \delta \rho^\ast \right\} d^3 \mathbf{x} \tag{39}\]

<p>ã§ã‚ã‚Šã€\(\delta\)ã¯ã‚ªã‚¤ãƒ©ãƒ¼çš„ãªæ‘‚å‹•é‡ã‚’è¡¨ã—ã¦ã„ã¾ã™ã€‚<br />
