<p>ã“ã“ã§ã€\(\delta \sigma_{ij}\) = 0.5( \nabla_i \delta v_j + \nabla_j \delta v_i - (2/3) g_{ij} \delta \theta)ã€\(\delta \theta = \nabla \cdot \delta \mathbf{v}\)ã§ã™ã€‚</p>

