\[\delta J_{\ell m} 
= \frac2c \left( \frac{\ell}{\ell +1}\right)^{1/2} \int r^\ell (\rho \delta v_i + v_i \delta \rho) \frac{r \epsilon^{ijk}}{\sqrt{\ell (\ell +1)}} \nabla_j Y_\ell^{\ast m} \nabla_k r d^3\mathbf{x} \tag{45}\]

